ğŸ’¡ Key Learnings & Highlights
Handling highly imbalanced datasets is critical in fraud detection

Accuracy alone is misleading; recall and cost-sensitive metrics are more meaningful

Ensemble learning (Random Forest, XGBoost) significantly improves robustness

End-to-end deployment requires strict alignment between training and inference

Real-world ML systems benefit from probability-based decisioning, not hard labels

